card.name: Alice, Otherworldly Visitor
card.flavor_text: "I've come to bring you back, you sly cat!"

card.name: Barrier of Faith
card.flavor_text: "It's futile." -Misteltein, the Pious Sword Saint

card.name: Blade of Faith
card.flavor_text: "The obstacles fate places before me do nothing to deter my faith!" -Misteltein, the Pious Sword Saint

card.name: Card Conscript
card.flavor_text: "Alright, line up in numerical order! Hey, you there! Can't you count?" -Alice, Otherworldly Visitor

card.name: Dark Alice Doll
card.flavor_text: "Aww, don't make such a sour face!" -Alice, Otherworldly Visitor

card.name: God's Choice
card.flavor_text: Brunhild's command is Lord Odin's decree.

card.name: March Hare of Valhalla
card.flavor_text: "Um, who?" -Alice, Otherworldly Visitor

card.name: Messenger of the Sun
card.flavor_text: Upon receiving the report from the messenger, Brunhild made the decision to attack Lunar Heaven.

card.name: Misteltein, the Pious Sword Saint
card.flavor_text: As time passed, her faith only grew. Now one with her belief, she returns to this world.

card.name: Monk Heroic Spirit
card.flavor_text: Misteltein's guardian, the heroic spirit of healing.

card.name: Musician of the Moon
card.flavor_text: "We were born with these large ears to enjoy music. I don't wish to lose this way of life." -Atom Seikhart

card.name: Mysterious Welcome Party
card.flavor_text: Atom was at a loss as to why they were holding a welcome party for an uninvited guest.

card.name: Palace Chef
card.flavor_text: In Lunar Heaven, it is believed carrots are best for one's health.

card.name: Reginleif, Inheritor of God's Will
card.flavor_text: Entrusted with god's mission, she leads the Valkyries to battle.

card.name: Spirit of Moonlit Nights
card.flavor_text: The moon of Lunar Heaven illuminated the ground, as if trying to tell something to the visitor.

card.name: Swordsman Heroic Spirit
card.flavor_text: Misteltein's devotee, the heroic spirit of faith.

card.name: The Battle of Sun and Moon
card.flavor_text: "Good heavens. We've got quite the visitors today." -Atom Seikhart

card.name: The Stranger from Re-Earth
card.flavor_text: "Don't expect me to hold a welcome party for an uninvited guest." -Atom Seikhart

card.name: Valkyrie of the Dawn
card.flavor_text: The Valkyries set their eyes on the moon, soaring higher than the sun.

card.name: Wizard Heroic Spirit
card.flavor_text: Misteltein's advisor, the heroic spirit of sorcery.

card.name: All Under Heaven Shall Perish
card.flavor_text: "The blue skies shall fade, dyed red by my stratagem!" -Zhuge Liang

card.name: Annihilation Dragon
card.flavor_text: When out of foes, this dragon will turn its fangs towards its own allies.

card.name: Frontline Warrior
card.flavor_text: Life is cheap during times of war.

card.name: Gaze of the Fire Emperor
card.flavor_text: Where Fu Xi goes, war always follows.

card.name: Ladies of the Three Stars
card.flavor_text: "I see! When working together, three people have the power of... well, three people working together." -Zhuge Liang

card.name: Lady Huang's Karakuri Soldier
card.flavor_text: The Karakuri obey no master. They merely destroy the enemy before them.

card.name: Ma'at, Arbiter of Judgment
card.flavor_text: "You may be able to outrun the blade. But nobody can outrun their sins."

card.name: Neo-Berserk Dragon
card.flavor_text: The return of madness.

card.name: Numbing Hedgehog
card.flavor_text: Momentary paralysis proves fatal.

card.name: Ruins Beneath the Sands
card.flavor_text: "This is it! Valhalla's sealed away power!" -Isis

card.name: Sand Awakening
card.flavor_text: "Rise! It is time to retake our glory!" -Isis

card.name: Sand Soldier
card.flavor_text: "The only thing more fragile than sand is human life itself." -Teachings of Sandora

card.name: Sandora's Invasion
card.flavor_text: "It's time. Let's go!" -Isis

card.name: Scales of the Ascendant
card.flavor_text: The scales incline towards the guilty.

card.name: Searing Wall of Sand
card.flavor_text: The scorching sands prove to be the greatest defense.

card.name: Sima Hui, the Crafty Tactician
card.flavor_text: "War without tactics is like a dumpling without fillings."

card.name: Surtr, the Sand Giant
card.flavor_text: Sealed beneath the sands, the embodiment of destruction.

card.name: The Three Kingdoms Partition Plan
card.flavor_text: "Shatter the Earth! Render them asunder!" -Zhuge Liang

card.name: Underhanded Assassin
card.flavor_text: In Sandora, poison is the preferred method of assassination.

card.name: Zhuge Liang
card.flavor_text: "Zhuge Liang. Pang Tong. It's said with one of these tacticians you can conquer a country. I'll show you that together we can conquer the very world."

card.name: Antorite, Sealed God of the Riverbed
card.flavor_text: "You're the one who freed me?... Fine. I suppose I'll help you out."

card.name: Bloodberry
card.flavor_text: Best be eaten fresh.

card.name: Diverse Evolution
card.flavor_text: "Become... something interesting!" -Loki

card.name: Guinevere, the Mobility Queen
card.flavor_text: In another world, a theater of only machines and humans, she was the last to live. Now the ruler of machines, she returns to this world.

card.name: Guinevere's Imperial Guard
card.flavor_text: These women will only heed the orders of one human being.

card.name: Mermaid of the Misty Spring
card.flavor_text: The mermaids were freed alongside Antorite and accompanied her on her journey.

card.name: Mordred, the Operator
card.flavor_text: Camelot's hardworking pilot.

card.name: Mutation Slime
card.flavor_text: In Misty Forest, the certain and the uncertain are one and the same.

card.name: Mystery Box
card.flavor_text: "What's in the box nya? What's in the box nya? Nya nya nya nya nyan!" -Schr?dinger

card.name: Parallel World Schrödinger
card.flavor_text: To escape from Alice, Schrödinger called upon his parallel selves.

card.name: Precision-Guided Munition, Sky Beat
card.flavor_text: Guinevere's range exceeds ten kilometers in circumference.

card.name: Ruins Submerged Beneath the Misty Spring
card.flavor_text: The ruins where Valhalla's mermaids sleep.

card.name: Schrödinger, the Harlequin of Phenomena
card.flavor_text: "To make certain the uncertain... that is my role. I a-paw-logize, Alice-nya. I can't leave with you yet."

card.name: Shackles of Mist
card.flavor_text: The mist hazes the heart.

card.name: Sky Round Musketeer
card.flavor_text: A machine's job is to be punctual and integral.

card.name: Skyfall
card.flavor_text: Guinevere descended at speeds faster than the eye could perceive.

card.name: Skynet
card.flavor_text: "Did you really think you could escape me?" -Guinevere, the Mobility Queen

card.name: Super Mobile Fortress Camelot
card.flavor_text: Guinevere led Camelot through the dimensions, finally arriving at Valhalla.

card.name: Teleport
card.flavor_text: The transfer of matter is not magic, but a fine science.

card.name: Wheel Drone
card.flavor_text: The wheel flies through the sky, even running over enemies at times.

card.name: Ancient Ruins Researcher
card.flavor_text: "I see mi-... This is quite the impressive discovery mi-."

card.name: Bullet Ball Thunder Clap
card.flavor_text: Who will become the bullet is often up for contention. In most cases, the one who falls asleep first is chosen.

card.name: Bunbuku, the Legendary Tea Kettle
card.flavor_text: "Transform? How rude. But, I will. Just for you."

card.name: Chamimi's Contemplation
card.flavor_text: Is she thinking or just sleeping? Nobody can ever tell.

card.name: Flying Squirrel
card.flavor_text: It may look cute, but the Mimi tribe knows its true danger.

card.name: Fox Shikigami
card.flavor_text: "Master, about the schedule for today..."

card.name: Friend Calling Whistle
card.flavor_text: A special tone only Ninjas can recognize.

card.name: Guardian Beast of Nature
card.flavor_text: The Mimi tribe was blown away when they discovered it. Not by the breathtaking ruins that laid beyond... but by the furious beast guarding it.

card.name: Liz, Sealed God of the Island
card.flavor_text: When Liz awoke, she felt no joy. She could sense her old friend had awakened to darkness.

card.name: Magellanica, the Ball Warrior
card.flavor_text: Since it's faster for him to roll to move, no one's ever seen him walk.

card.name: Molmol, King of Rare Beasts
card.flavor_text: Chamimi approached the King of Beasts, attempting to communicate with it.

card.name: Ninja Students
card.flavor_text: "These children are the seeds of the future." -Hanzo

card.name: Rikyu, Cat Tongued Tea Master
card.flavor_text: When Rikyu came to Kouga from another world he offered tea to the villagers. But no one would accept it. As it would turn out, cats can't drink hot drinks.

card.name: Ruins Beneath the Flora
card.flavor_text: Slipping past the guardian beast's pursuit, the Mimi tribe took a determined step into the ruins.

card.name: Seimei's Disciple
card.flavor_text: "Unfortunately, Master Seimei is sleeping right now. Not even I know when he will awake."

card.name: Storm Cat
card.flavor_text: "Can you keep up with my movements?" -Hanzo

card.name: Table Flip
card.flavor_text: "This tea's too hot to drink!!" -Rikyu, Cat Tongued Tea Master

card.name: The Six Jizo Statues
card.flavor_text: While it may take time, they will always return the favor.

card.name: The Unsealing of God
card.flavor_text: The Mimi tribe came to worship Liz, for she looked exactly like the gods as described in their ancient songs.

card.name: Tsunade, Brawny Cat Ninja
card.flavor_text: "With some guts and strength, you can do anything!"

card.name: Amon, Conspirer of Atrocities
card.flavor_text: He feels nothing but joy. Joy at being given another chance to bring ruin.

card.name: Astema, the Returnee of Hatred
card.flavor_text: As time passed, her hatred only grew. Now one with her malice, she returns to this world.

card.name: Athenia, Sealed God of the Ruins
card.flavor_text: "A most terrible awakening... for me and this world."

card.name: Black-Eyed Angel
card.flavor_text: No light shone in their eyes, their hearts long since enveloped in darkness.

card.name: Caspiel, the Fallen Angel of Rebellion
card.flavor_text: Satan's will transformed into a strong impulse, stirring the fallen angels to action.

card.name: Chaining Hatred
card.flavor_text: Hatred, a disease plaguing the hearts of many.

card.name: Contract Demon
card.flavor_text: The contract will always be fulfilled. For demons love to collect.

card.name: Corrupt Teachings
card.flavor_text: "The time has come. We must supervise this world in place of God." -Lucifer

card.name: Dark Soldier of the Fallen
card.flavor_text: They despise humans blessed by light the most.

card.name: Dragon Zombie
card.flavor_text: Lost in jealousy, its heart and wings have long since given in to the darkness.

card.name: Graveyard Vampire
card.flavor_text: The lone vampire could not read Oborozuki's intentions. For reasons unknown, she came to this area and seized control.

card.name: March of the Dead
card.flavor_text: The parade marched onward to the meeting place of the wanderers.

card.name: Orchard of the Immortals
card.flavor_text: The only land to bear fruit on this ruined earth.

card.name: Orpheus, the Immortal Player
card.flavor_text: "Beautiful. So this is the sound of Valhalla." -Oborozuki

card.name: Power of Immortality
card.flavor_text: Corruption only strengthens the undead.

card.name: Ruined Earth
card.flavor_text: The liberator's nature influenced the sealed god's power, corrupting Athenia's power of harvest into something new, something... impure.

card.name: Ruins Devil
card.flavor_text: These little devils love doing what others hate.

card.name: Sewing Zombie
card.flavor_text: Memories from life prove most helpful in death.

card.name: Soul Prison
card.flavor_text: Only hatred can unlock this prison.

card.name: Specter of the Abyss
card.flavor_text: Specters are the rulers of the night.
